mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c96cc5f3688029f91b535f00b150a285fa39a9","tid":1099313,"uid":152790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e24841ef511c79cf55f44a1c1d254137998329e","tid":1099313,"uid":152790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"3M咩PR70唔記得左<br />\n幫屋企人整左兩幅落地窗一幅7000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n透光得黎隔熱又唔反光<br />\n幾好<br />\n<br />\n自己屋企就淘寶貨5分一價錢<br />\n隔熱都ok<br />\n不過變暗左同有少少反光"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:33:05.000Z","msg":"3m就代理貼埋又快又靚<br />\n自己貼好易有泡<br />\n<br />\n不過價錢差好遠<br />\n<br />\n要揀隔UV100%<br />\n隔IR越高越隔熱<br />\n隔可見光越高就越唔透明<br />\n通常越透明但隔熱就越貴"},{"pid":"bf841b80ff89a8b65dadec4d9083919cc236d617","tid":1099313,"uid":152790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b329616f05ed58071a0c4684c539dde89c59c3","tid":1099313,"uid":146041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e24841ef511c79cf55f44a1c1d254137998329e","tid":1099313,"uid":152790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"3M咩PR70唔記得左<br />\n幫屋企人整左兩幅落地窗一幅7000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n透光得黎隔熱又唔反光<br />\n幾好<br />\n<br />\n自己屋企就淘寶貨5分一價錢<br />\n隔熱都ok<br />\n不過變暗左同有少少反光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"我搵師傅打過價， 都係咁上下， 貴到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:35:59.000Z","msg":"一分錢一分貨<br />\n如果覺得太貴就淘寶<br />\n比得起就3m啦唔駛煩"},{"pid":"f616bd1e035b59c215e065ac6957fb0c4577bf8a","tid":1099313,"uid":5020,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f5f16210741c09b8e493e1fffec3eab44fa5d705","tid":1099313,"uid":146041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"樓上自己貼既ching,  有無技巧或者經驗分享?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"3M隔熱貼都有分好多種架，我以前做工程都幫客搵3M師傅貼過<br />\n<br />\n自己DIY果條line 叫3M Scotch思高隔熱玻璃膜(又稱EN系列)，香港家陣買到既係EN94<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43QCE2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43QCE2O.jpg&h=3dea63ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大細75x90cm一塊，有分1盒1塊($~400)、1盒2塊($~600)、1盒4塊(唔知幾錢，無問)<br />\n買得越多相對越平<br />\n但留意返，佢只係得阻隔60%紅外線及45%紫外線，降熱率好低唔夠一半<br />\n<br />\n而如果你搵3M師傅貼既係3M Prestige系列(又稱PR系列)<br />\n要上門度呎，一般平方呎由$60到$80，睇你揀PR幾多，同室外貼定室內貼<br />\n由PR40到PR70，越高越好隔熱，但相對會越黑<br />\n都可以阻隔97%紅外線及99.9%紫外線，降熱率有一半<br />\n仲有D商用既會有鏡面效果（外面望唔到入面），但呢D一般唔會貼去家用(因為好易畀人投訴)<br />\n<br />\n另外，留意最好搵一搵物管問下畀唔畀貼，有D私樓係唔畀改變窗口顏色<br />\n<br />\n而大陸淘寶果D多數係假貨<br />\n當時有個裝修師傅拎過佢另外幫客貼既大陸淘寶所謂3M貼既淨料畀我試<br />\n得個黑字完全唔隔熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adce013fd5ea731ea592d7c5ba774308bf15b45","tid":1099313,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4620594a4db2fa8d766610c5026ecf64eb306c07","tid":1099313,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0adce013fd5ea731ea592d7c5ba774308bf15b45","tid":1099313,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:08:13.000Z","msg":"3m都有分好多line架喎<br />\ncrystalline望到，有分透光度<br />\n其他唔知"},{"pid":"fe9a61292270c1b3374e172bb39c100e9f944eb7","tid":1099313,"uid":146041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:07:57.000Z","msg":"推一推post,  上星期六終於搵左師傅貼， 二房埋單差不多一皮。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢幾日陰天， 比較唔到。 遲下夏天再報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1678dc501bfb02